Allow us to introduce the BRIDES Top Tier Salons for 2025–2026—a nationwide directory of editor-vetted and -approved bridal boutiques designed to help you find the one. 👗✨

Organized by region and highlighting specialties like budget-friendly, plus-size selections, and more, this guide is your starting point for saying yes to the dress—tap the link in our bio to start browsing. 🤍

latestPosts.caption:
BRIDES Getaway Guide ✈️: @cobblerscovehotel

If you’re looking for a Caribbean honeymoon destination that ensures you never have to leave the resort, look no further than @cobblerscovehotel. This boutique hotel is located right on the sandy beaches of #Barbados and offers an intimate feel with attentive service in a relaxed atmosphere. 

@brides social media director @yagirlstar  gave us a glimpse into this historic and cozy resort. Highlights include private dining experiences, boat tours, and high tea every afternoon 🫖 For tips to book your honeymoon (or next vacation) tap the link in bio. 

#carribean #cobblerscove #boutiquehotel #beach #sunset

Meet the Vendor: @studiomondine 🤍

For the first highlight of AAPI Heritage Month we’re putting the spotlight on @studiomondine, a floral design studio led by Amanda Luu. 💐 Rooted in a practice of observation and reverence for nature the studio uses a contemporary lens to approach floral design as a dialogue between the built and natural environments. Their clients become creative partners, resulting in work that is intentional, ephemeral, and deeply reflective of place and time. 

Learn more about the floral designers @studiomondine. ✨

📷 (slide #2): @normanandblake
